{"type": "article", "id": 36318, "title": "内衣品牌“大内密探”要卖，以及，推荐APC的男装新系列 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-03T02:51:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 442, "name": "HUMAN MADE"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 24445, "name": "A.P.C"}, {"id": 36398, "name": "Mastermind"}, {"id": 36399, "name": "罗博报告"}, {"id": 441, "name": "NIGO"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170103094505LWMlrPq2h0QtC8Vo.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/agent-provocateur-company-for-sale/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>伦敦高级内衣品牌 Agent Provocateur 可能要卖</b></a> | Agent Provocateur（大内密探）创立于 1994 年，由英国时装女王 Vivienne Westwood 的儿子Joseph Corre 和妻子 Serena Reese 共同创立。私募基金 3i 曾在 2007 年斥资 6000 万英镑买下了 Agent Provocateur 80% 的股份，后因不合时宜的扩张计划导致困损。3i 曾在 2014 年想要出售 Agent Provocateur，但并未成功。泰晤士报援引零售业内人士的说法，称 Agent Provocateur 目前至少值 1500 万英镑。但品牌方面并未给出回应。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/business/mergers-acquisitions/pmc-robb-report-joint-venture-rockbridge-deal-luxury-magazine-290452/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Penske 传媒联合 Rockbridge 资本，收购《罗博报告》杂志</b></a> | Rockbridge 曾在 2014 年收购了有着四十余年历史的高端生活杂志《罗博报告》。现在，经营着 20 多家媒体，Variety、FN、 TVLine.com 等媒体的母公司 Penske 传媒集团，也加入对《罗博报告》的收购中。但双方目前并未透露收购细节。</p><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/business/mergers-acquisitions/iconix-brand-group-sells-sharper-image-threesixty-100-million-divestiture-mergers-acquisitions-290679/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国品牌管理公司 Iconix 出售旗下品牌 Sharper Image</b></a> | Iconix 在上周五表示，公司同意将 Sharper Image 品牌及相关知识产权的权利出售给 ThreeSixty Group ，交易额为 1 亿美元。该公司表示，ThreeSixty Group 是该品牌的最大被授权商。这笔交易在 12 月 30 日完成，交易所得及额外现金将用于偿付大约 1.15 亿美元的债务。Iconix 成立于 1992 年，是一个拥有一系列时尚、运动、家纺及动漫品牌，业务包括奢侈品及大众市场的零售分销。Sharper Image 则是一家创新消费品供应商，目前有 300 多个零售网点。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Converse 发布鸡年限定系列。全系列共有黑色基调的 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/converse-year-of-the-rooster-black-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Black Pack </a>以及主打彩色的 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/converse-year-of-the-rooster-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chuck Taylor All Star </a>两个版本，将于 1 月 3 日登陆 Converse 官网，并于 1 月 6 日在指定线下门店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701030847052gWFK1a7jzh06mNP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084707ratjqWlwg6Y32iev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103085348JTkZPmHbFWB8Ert0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103085603TiJNE9DVCmLRKdHP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103085817eaJMdI6S9miszOr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103090406h0z1CyjZ5nAHWlQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103090420HQ6xePh5vizIf8LO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103090423e20VwcTgMEjDkFGf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103090434oEUXRwObVCHFP0Ic.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103090437nTJDfbo1vr82l6gX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017010309043971ntrFmdO6lkBGCU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/mastermind-japan-launching-mastermind-world\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本潮牌 Mastermind 将启动全新副牌 Mastermind World</a>，该副牌将面向全球市场，根据不同的市场差异推出与 Mastermind Japan 不同的剪裁和设计。据称，这个品牌还将在 2017 巴黎时装周上发布它的秋冬系列。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091038rJDtHPVgqlsAFwk3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在迎来男装系列 30 周年之际，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/a-p-c-2017a-p-c-us-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">法国品牌 A.P.C 发布名为 A.P.C US 的 2017 春夏系列男装</a>，该系列从素材到制作全部在美国完成，将于 1 月起陆续在各大城市上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084435bweT53oK0RtL4pCu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084436eLM8vgatNAozpSnT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084439XIwpJs8fOzbKAV53.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084441JogwrmNEi9yLZcz7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084445vdHEgtl13qWGXmp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084447Dzoh7LVW0E5QsmaC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701030844504F6L1EpmZlVJkIfy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084450nWw0Xc4ZUeOirIf6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084513f2sFzVu5T9l4NABk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084517hTPgfDrJLR93YveK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084522IGsTQBvKNdHkWmJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103084537jQVnRxUkl5rqBATD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">过节送礼的话，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/louis-vuitton-the-art-of-giving-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">LV 的 The Art of Giving 2017 全新配件系列</a>也许是个还不错的选择。该系列包括了铅笔、笔筒、笔记本、收纳盒、随身镜等多个单品，在设计上采用了金属细节搭配高级皮革，价格低至 94 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091055LJYxVzWFcEoSMQf8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091056rVzPKN2Lag5mUHp0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091056gcxjRWNtGH6hEC5q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091057M45gN7TOjd3hkRyV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091058EG5dw3oh7mM1YkVa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091059XDuAEal9FcJtmryY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701030910597vVsDWwNHRjGaiA2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701030910597yEQl1vi4RdSaFor.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091059AIXNE6uhTalGYxOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701030912089R0Z46Pcy5hzaLdA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">日本潮牌&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/human-made-spring-summer-2017-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Human Made 发布 2017 春夏系列</a>，新系列继续以 GEARS FOR FUTURISTIC TEENAGERS 为主题，并由品牌主理人 NIGO 亲自出镜演绎。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091233EnkrM8Tzmh27sPAw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091233UBN2SfcTr0Eye3u7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091233qKevOYf7IDtHZsX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091234cX9xAiE7BV5knSut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091234spzZErdGvmjQYLty.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091237yJTjh25oXSHY76AG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091240gjCdlPtVpemoDN1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091242wqOWFJRQaHEP9rAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091242B7HYVP2QFZCXsOiE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091244JuvBcRC9MWixwy7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091245Ky3rAMspkuFNO609.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170103091245ZICgcHDsbmhVJvyB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/converse-year-of-the-rooster-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> hypebeast</a><br></p>"}